870
00:38:17,076 --> 00:38:18,115
Your Su family

871
00:38:18,116 --> 00:38:19,995
is indeed a family of generals.

872
00:38:19,996 --> 00:38:21,667
Thank you for your praise, Your Majesty.

873
00:38:22,596 --> 00:38:24,276
This is Official Lu,

874
00:38:24,277 --> 00:38:26,306
