936
00:40:35,357 --> 00:40:37,236
What exactly had happened?

937
00:40:37,237 --> 00:40:38,276
How did she die?

938
00:40:38,277 --> 00:40:39,107
Yes, tell us.

939
00:40:39,396 --> 00:40:40,836
When her body was found,

940
00:40:40,837 --> 00:40:42,627
