996
00:42:55,637 --> 00:42:57,067
I thought you were...

997
00:42:57,237 --> 00:42:58,466
I'm all right.

998
00:43:01,116 --> 00:43:03,266
Fortunately, I didn't fail Mrs. Li

999
00:43:03,317 --> 00:43:04,716
