1000
00:43:04,717 --> 00:43:05,915
Thank you, Official Zhou.

1001
00:43:05,916 --> 00:43:07,627
I'm extremely grateful.

1002
00:43:08,996 --> 00:43:09,716
Zhen,

1003
00:43:09,717 --> 00:43:11,466
